>>>channel, date and time information. As you may know, this is a convenient
>>>tool for programming your VCR, ie, without experiencing the agony
>>>interface that most VCR mfgrs reinvent. (They're good at it.)

>>>But, I don't always have the Sunday TV section available.... So, is there
